description:
Starts the presentation slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("StartSlideShow");
```

Pauses the current slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("PauseSlideShow");
```

Resumes the current slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("ResumeSlideShow");
```

Ends the current slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("EndSlideShow");
```

Displays the slide following the current slide in the slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("GoToNextSlideInSlideShow");
```

Displays the slide following the current slide in the slide show.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
window.Asc.plugin.executeMethod ("GoToPreviousSlideInSlideShow");
```

Displays the slide with the specific index.

## Try it

 ```js document-builder={"documentType": "slide"}
